data.enText: belonging or relating separately to each of the people or things already mentioned

data.chText: 他们在各自的领域都被视为专家。
data.enText: They are each recognized specialists in their respective fields.

data.chText: 男女在社会中各自的角色
data.enText: the respective roles of men and women in society

value.def: Respective means relating or belonging separately to the individual people you have just mentioned.

example.ex: Steve and I were at very different stages in our respective careers...
example.tran: 史蒂夫和我在各自的职业生涯中处于迥然不同的阶段。

example.ex: They went into their respective bedrooms to pack.
example.tran: 他们回到各自的卧室打包。
